body:
Does the onnx checker believe the model to be valid? That's not a guarantee it is, but it's a starting point.

Add this before the onnx.save:

`onnx.checker.check_model(model, True)`

I added `onnx.checker.check_model(model, True)` before `onnx.save`, but it raised no error.
ONNX Runtime still fails to load the model.
